   "endLine": 88,
   "source": "<ROUTINE SALT-F (\"OPT\" (CONTEXT <>) \"AUX\" X)\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? .CONTEXT ,M-OBJDESC>\n\t\t<TELL CA ,SALT \" is seated before \" A ,EASEL\n\t\t      \", dabbing color onto \" A ,CANVAS>\n\t\t<COND (<SEE-ANYTHING-IN? ,SALT>\n\t\t       <TELL \". He's holding \">\n\t\t       <CONTENTS ,SALT>)>\n\t\t<TELL C ,PER>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? .CONTEXT ,M-WINNER>\n\t\t<COND (<AND <VERB? HELLO>\n\t\t\t    <PRSO? ROOMS SALT>>\n\t\t       <GREET-SAILOR>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)\n\t\t      (<AND <VERB? TELL-ABOUT SSHOW>\n\t\t\t    <PRSO? ME>>\n\t\t       <ASK-SALT-ABOUT ,PRSI>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)\n\t\t      (<OR <VERB? EXAMINE WHAT WHO WHERE>\n\t\t\t   <AND <VERB? SHOW>\n\t\t\t\t<PRSI? ME>>>\n\t\t       <ASK-SALT-ABOUT ,PRSO>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)\n\t\t      (<AND <VERB? GIVE GET-FOR>\n\t\t\t    <PRSI? ME>>\n\t\t       <ASK-SALT-FOR ,PRSO>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)\n\t\t      (<AND <VERB? SGIVE SGET-FOR>\n\t\t\t    <PRSO? ME>>\n\t\t       <ASK-SALT-FOR ,PRSI>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)>\n\t\t<DEAF-SALT>\n\t\t<RFATAL>)\n\t       (<T? .CONTEXT>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (<THIS-PRSI?>\n\t\t<COND (<VERB? THROW THROW-OVER>\n\t\t       <HARMLESS ,PRSI>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (<VERB? GIVE GET-FOR>\n\t\t       <GIVE-TO-SALT ,PRSO>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (<VERB? SHOW>\n\t\t       <DO-GLANCE ,SALT ,PRSO>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (<VERB? TELL>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (<VERB? EXAMINE>\n\t\t<TELL CTHEO \"'s ice-blue eyes glance up from his work.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? YELL>\n\t\t<NOT-DEAF>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? ASK-FOR>\n\t\t<ASK-SALT-FOR ,PRSI>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? ASK-ABOUT>\n\t\t<ASK-SALT-ABOUT ,PRSI>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? TELL-ABOUT>\n\t\t<DO-GLANCE ,SALT ,PRSI>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? HELLO GOODBYE WAVE-AT>\n\t\t<GREET-SAILOR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<SET X <HURTING?>>\n\t\t<HARMLESS>\n\t        <RTRUE>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>>"
