   "source": "<ROUTINE CLERIC-F (\"OPT\" (CONTEXT <>) \"AUX\" X)\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? .CONTEXT ,M-OBJDESC>\n\t\t<TELL CTHE ,CLERIC \n\" is here, surrounded by a grateful crowd of villagers. He's holding \">\n\t\t<CONTENTS ,CLERIC>\n\t\t<TELL C ,PER>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? .CONTEXT ,M-CONT>\n\t\t<COND (<SET X <TOUCHING?>>\n\t\t       <NOT-SO-FAST ,CLERIC>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? .CONTEXT ,M-WINNER>\n\t\t<COND (<AND <VERB? HELLO>\n\t\t\t    <PRSO? ROOMS CLERIC>>\n\t\t       <GREET-CLERIC>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)\n\t\t      (<AND <VERB? TELL-ABOUT SSHOW>\n\t\t\t    <PRSO? ME>>\n\t\t       <ASK-CLERIC-ABOUT ,PRSI>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)\n\t\t      (<OR <VERB? EXAMINE WHAT WHO WHERE>\n\t\t\t   <AND <VERB? SHOW>\n\t\t\t\t<PRSI? ME>>>\n\t\t       <ASK-CLERIC-ABOUT ,PRSO>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)\n\t\t      (<AND <VERB? GIVE GET-FOR>\n\t\t\t    <PRSI? ME>>\n\t\t       <ASK-CLERIC-FOR ,PRSO>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)\n\t\t      (<AND <VERB? SGIVE SGET-FOR>\n\t\t\t    <PRSO? ME>>\n\t\t       <ASK-CLERIC-FOR ,PRSI>\n\t\t       <RFATAL>)>\n\t\t<TELL \"\\\"Your accent is strange. I don't understand.\\\"\" CR>\n\t\t<RFATAL>)\n\t       (<THIS-PRSI?>\n\t\t<COND (<VERB? THROW THROW-OVER>\n\t\t       <HARMLESS ,PRSI>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (<VERB? GIVE GET-FOR>\n\t\t       <GIVE-TO-CLERIC ,PRSO>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)\n\t\t      (<VERB? SHOW>\n\t\t       <DO-GLANCE ,CLERIC ,PRSO>\n\t\t       <RTRUE>)>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (<VERB? TELL>\n\t\t<COND (<T? ,P-CONT>\n\t\t       <RFALSE>)>\n\t\t<NO-RESPONSE>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? EXAMINE>\n\t\t<TELL \"He\">\n\t\t<COND (<SEE-ANYTHING-IN?>\n\t\t       <TELL \"'s holding \">\n\t\t       <CONTENTS>\n\t\t       <TELL \", and\">)>\n\t\t<TELL \" looks as if he hasn't slept for days.\" CR>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? ASK-FOR>\n\t\t<ASK-CLERIC-FOR ,PRSI>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? ASK-ABOUT>\n\t\t<ASK-CLERIC-ABOUT ,PRSI>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? TELL-ABOUT>\n\t\t<DO-GLANCE ,CLERIC ,PRSI>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<VERB? HELLO WAVE-AT>\n\t\t<GREET-CLERIC>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<SET X <HURTING?>>\n\t\t<HARMLESS>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>>"
