   "source": "<ROUTINE GET-NAME (\"AUX\" CNT PTR APO DASH BAD ANY CAP SPACE LEN X CHAR)\n\t <COND (<NOT <IS? ,PLAYER ,NAMED>>\n\t\t<COPYT ,DEFAULT-NAME ,CHARNAME ,DEFAULT-NAME-LENGTH>)>\n\t <TELL CR \n\"Finally, you must select a Name for your character.|\n|\nBy what Name shall your character be known?\">\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t    <COPYT ,P-INBUF 0 ,P-INBUF-LENGTH>\n\t    <PUTB ,P-INBUF 0 %<- ,P-INBUF-LENGTH 2>>\n\t    <TELL CR CR \"[The default is \\\"\">\n\t    <PRINT-TABLE ,CHARNAME>\n\t    <TELL \".\\\"] >\">\n\t    <REPEAT ()\n\t       <COLOR ,INCOLOR ,BGND>\n\t       <SET X <READ ,P-INBUF 0>>\n\t       <COND (<EQUAL? .X ,EOL ,LF>\n\t\t      <RETURN>)>\n\t       <SOUND 2>>\n\t    <COLOR ,FORE ,BGND>\n\t    <SET LEN <GETB ,P-INBUF 1>>\n\t    <COND (<ZERO? .LEN>\n\t\t   <RETURN>)>\t\t \n\t    <SET X <+ .LEN 1>>\n\t    <SET PTR 2>\n\t    <SET APO 0>\n\t    <SET DASH 0>\n\t    <SET BAD 0>\n\t    <SET ANY 0>\n\t    <REPEAT ()\n\t       <SET CHAR <GETB ,P-INBUF .PTR>>\n\t       <COND (<AND <G? .CHAR %<- <ASCII !\\a> 1>>\n\t\t\t   <L? .CHAR %<+ <ASCII !\\z> 1>>>\n\t\t      <INC ANY>)\n\t\t     (<EQUAL? .CHAR ,SP>)\n\t\t     (<EQUAL? .CHAR %<ASCII !\\'>>\n\t\t      <INC APO>)\n\t\t     (<EQUAL? .CHAR %<ASCII !\\->>\n\t\t      <INC DASH>)\n\t\t     (T\n\t\t      <INC BAD>\n\t\t      <RETURN>)>\n\t       <COND (<IGRTR? PTR .X>\n\t\t      <RETURN>)>>\n\t    <COND (<OR <ZERO? .ANY>\n\t\t       <T? .BAD>\n\t\t       <G? .APO 1>\n\t\t       <G? .DASH 1>>\n\t\t   <BAD-NAME \"silly\">\n\t\t   <AGAIN>)\t       \n\t\t  (<G? .LEN ,CHARNAME-LENGTH>\n\t\t   <BAD-NAME \"too long\">\n\t\t   <AGAIN>)>\n\t    <COPYT ,CHARNAME 0 %<+ ,CHARNAME-LENGTH 1>>\n\t    <SET CNT 0>\n\t    <SET PTR 2>\n\t    <SET CAP 1>\n\t    <SET SPACE 0>\n\t    <SET ANY 0>\n\t    <REPEAT ()\n\t       <SET CHAR <GETB ,P-INBUF .PTR>>\n\t       <COND (<EQUAL? .CHAR ,SP>\n\t\t      <INC CAP>\n\t\t      <INC SPACE>\n\t\t      <COND (<AND <T? .ANY>\n\t\t\t\t  <EQUAL? .SPACE 1>>\n\t\t\t     <INC CNT>\n\t\t\t     <PUTB ,CHARNAME .CNT ,SP>)>)\n\t\t     (T\n\t\t      <INC ANY>\n\t\t      <SET SPACE 0>\n\t\t      <COND (<EQUAL? .CHAR %<ASCII !\\'>\n\t\t\t\t           %<ASCII !\\->>\n\t\t\t     <INC CAP>)\n\t\t\t    (<T? .CAP>\n\t\t\t     <SET CAP 0>\n\t\t\t     <SET CHAR <- .CHAR ,SP>>)>\n\t\t      <INC CNT>\n\t\t      <PUTB ,CHARNAME .CNT .CHAR>)>\n\t       <COND (<IGRTR? PTR .X>\n\t\t      <RETURN>)>>\n\t    <PUTB ,CHARNAME 0 .CNT>\n\t    <TELL CR \"Is \\\"\">\n\t    <PRINT-TABLE ,CHARNAME>\n\t    <TELL \"\\\" correct?\">\n\t    <COND (<YES?>\n\t\t   <RETURN>)>\n\t    <BAD-NAME \"cast into the void\">>\n\t <MAKE ,PLAYER ,NAMED>\n\t <SHOW-RANK ,WIDTH>\n\t <RFALSE>>"
