   "source": "<ROUTINE TO-SPLENDOR (\"OPT\" WHO \"AUX\" DIR X Y)\n\t <PUTP ,IN-SPLENDOR ,P?FNUM <GETP ,HERE ,P?FNUM>>\n\t <SET DIR ,P?NW>\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t    <SET X ,SORRY-EXIT>\n\t    <SET Y \"Lush vegetation blocks your path.\">\n\t    <COND (<PROB 50>\n\t\t   <SET X %<+ ,CONNECT 9 ,MARKBIT>>\n\t\t   <SET Y ,IN-SPLENDOR>)>\n\t    <NEW-EXIT? ,IN-SPLENDOR .DIR .X .Y>\n\t    <COND (<IGRTR? DIR ,P?NORTH>\n\t\t   <RETURN>)>>\n\t <SAFE-VEHICLE-EXIT>\n\t <MOVE ,HERD ,IN-SPLENDOR>\n\t <QUEUE ,I-MARE-SEES 3>\n\t <DESCRIBE-GATE>\n\t <CARRIAGE-RETURNS>\n\t <GOTO ,IN-SPLENDOR>\n\t <RTRUE>>"
